    <string name="about_title">About</string>
    <string name="about_app_desc">Xia\'s Addons is a powerful toolkit designed to unlock the full potential of your device. It bridges the gap between complex system modifications and user-friendly control, offering granular management of hardware resources.</string>
    
    <string name="about_features_header">KEY FEATURES</string>
    <string name="about_feat_perf">Performance Profiling</string>
    <string name="about_feat_perf_desc">Advanced CPU/GPU frequency scaling and governor management.</string>
    <string name="about_feat_identity">Identity Spoofing</string>
    <string name="about_feat_identity_desc">Bypass Play Integrity checks and unlock app-specific features.</string>
    <string name="about_feat_power">Power Management</string>
    <string name="about_feat_power_desc">Bypass charging and thermal safety controls.</string>

    <string name="about_safety_header">SAFETY &amp; DEFAULTS</string>
    <string name="about_safety_title">Why Defaults Matter</string>
    <string name="about_safety_desc">The default configurations are tuned for stability and safety. Advanced modules like Undervolting and Thermal overrides are powerful but risky. We recommend sticking to the "Balanced" profiles unless you understand the hardware implications.</string>

